      <title>债券收益率跳高，因为国防承诺世界各地的波纹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/bond-yields-rise-as-defense-promises-ripple-around-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，欧洲领导人讨论了对乌克兰的支持，并改善了对非洲大陆的安全措施，促使投资者为国防支出的激增做准备，债券收益率上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/bond-yields-rise-as-defense-promises-ripple-around-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:20:14 GMT</pubDate>
